{"tid":140321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"剛抓到稀有精靈「拉普拉斯」　新加坡阿公心臟病死亡","createTime":"2017-03-02T05:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T18:46:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae6d3397832df5dff9bfda096cb0f4d0105323cb","tid":140321,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:56:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170301/875326.htm?ercamp=sorted_hot_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170301%2F875326.htm%3Fercamp%3Dsorted_hot_news&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=95166147\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170301/875326.htm?ercamp=sorted_hot_news</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2364/2364013.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2364%2F2364013.jpg&h=ab7dc6f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">▲剛抓到拉普拉斯和布盧皇，星國阿公心臟病亡。（圖／翻攝自神奇寶貝百科）</span><br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n2017年03月1日 16:15<br />\n風靡全球的遊戲《寵物小精靈Go》，近日風光推出第二代，吸引不少玩家繼續抓寶！新加坡1名67歲梁姓老翁迷上《寵物小精靈Go》，每天都與朋友一同外出抓寶，上月26日傍晚出門抓寶時，卻因心臟病發不幸過世。<br />\n<br />\n據新加坡《聯合早報》報導，死者妻子陳瑪麗表示，丈夫愛玩寶可夢，自從推出後每天都到金沙和志同道合的朋友一同「抓寶」，案發當天一家人還一起慶祝姐姐生日，吃飽回家後，丈夫表示要出門抓精靈。<br />\n<br />\n陳瑪麗指出，傍晚6點接到醫院來電，要家人去見他最後一面，就知道不妙了。她拿出丈夫生前的手機，顯示梁姓老翁心臟病發前，正在金沙抓精靈，還抓到一隻稀有的拉普拉斯（Lapras）和第二代精靈布盧皇（Granbull）。<br />\n<br />\n她也無奈透露，丈夫每天機不離手，一發現有稀有精靈，無論多遠都會去，為了能更快抓到寶，還特地把手機換成最新款的，曾多次提醒他不要這麼賣命，但他都充耳不聞，「如果他肯聽勸，今天就不會這樣了。」"},{"pid":"34e02d0e7a590df994fb2c2be1ee838fd8a3b4e8","tid":140321,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e958c29ff9b60ea464d4f286342d2e891d3299","tid":140321,"uid":15777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:05:38.000Z","msg":"睇到標題 心諗乜撚係拉普拉斯"},{"pid":"36a57d1391fab0e14a7cbb14953455daeb749b81","tid":140321,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:06:16.000Z","msg":"好過d廢老"},{"pid":"1fd566a4e8cfaf37c7a2a850e819d2dc9f7d00f3","tid":140321,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:08:42.000Z","msg":"譯得寵物小精靈，隻野就叫番背背龍啦屌你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25c4869a0aa6e6dbe884b9ab0c02e707b60689c","tid":140321,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:10:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>譯得寵物小精靈，隻野就叫番背背龍啦</blockquote><br />\n無玩開寵物小精靈唔知呢隻叫背背龍,sorry"},{"pid":"c4dff9dc07e16fc0a185e49043ee8476c0b775f3","tid":140321,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>譯得寵物小精靈，隻野就叫番背背龍啦</blockquote><br />\n無玩開寵物小精靈唔知呢隻叫背背龍,sorry</blockquote><br />\n有玩開都冇可能知"},{"pid":"c01a9af30595b0de1e07d9f27e406b8443356b57","tid":140321,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:21:12.000Z","msg":"如果係IV100靚技班吉拉LV30"},{"pid":"738f46e07fc5a83d63af27d9a1285f8577dfcc9b","tid":140321,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   人地抄台灣新聞過嚟 ,  用台譯有乜問題<br />\n<br />\n樓上ON 9 9 又鬧人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2443c73ecb1da9c6db31184d5437bee09c6736d","tid":140321,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb2525d0eb2ef240c15203f0e920a4a3420a932","tid":140321,"uid":2649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:43:42.000Z","msg":"<block